    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find. It has been meticulously maintained, garage-kept, and shows no signs of wear inside or out. The paint is flawless with a deep, original shine, and the interior retains its factory-fresh appearance and scent. Mechanically, it is perfect, with all service records up to date, ensuring a smooth and reliable driving experience for the next owner. You will not find a more pristine example of this model on the market.",
